Model equation for RUSLE:
A = R⋅ K ⋅ LS ⋅ C

R = erosivity of the rainfall in MJ ⋅ mm ⋅ ha-1 ⋅ h-1 ⋅ yr-1
K = erodibility of the soil in t ⋅ ha ⋅ h ⋅ ha-1 ⋅ MJ-1 ⋅ mm-1
LS = topography
C = cover management factor

R: https://lew.epa.gov/
K: https://websoilsurvey.nrcs.usda.gov/app/WebSoilSurvey.aspx
